,"msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/201046_46fd4392f3f4cb9a977d18a0c4a31030.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F201046_46fd4392f3f4cb9a977d18a0c4a31030.jpg&h=16ab0f26&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/201047_30c2c31d0b7af4ad8cfede0ae4769b63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F201047_30c2c31d0b7af4ad8cfede0ae4769b63.jpg&h=d20e472c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/201048_3c9ed7ce35db27c7efcb7eb77ffdfc03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F201048_3c9ed7ce35db27c7efcb7eb77ffdfc03.jpg&h=4167ecf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個依島先生 硬係覺得佢係個伏筆<br />\n佢同夏目兩個都好在意對方 有熟悉既感覺<br />\n而且佢年紀又大 <br />\n同夏目又似樣<br />\n我覺得佢可能同夏目既外公有d關係</blockquote><br />\n我個人覺得佢就係外公嘅可能性好大<br />\n因為依島先生年齡符合 (名取有話佢年紀都幾大同可能唔係人)<br />\n貓咪老師係佢同夏目互相認識嘅時候又特登stop左佢地<br />\n名取問佢知唔知友人帳嘅事時佢嘅表情似係知情<br />\n只係唔知點解佢認唔到夏目<br />\n不過解釋唔到箱崎先生嘅式神講話佢遇過似夏目嘅男人依件事<br />\n因為可能係畫風問題 我唔覺得夏目似依島先生"}]}